Package lawnlayer

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PowerUp
    An interface for all power ups in the game.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    The game engine.
    Boost
    A singleton subclass of GameObject and implementation of PowerUp.
    Enemy
    A subclass of Entity governing the behaviours of all enemy types in the game.
    Entity
    An abstract subclass of GameObject governing the behaviours of all entities in the game.
    Freeze
    A singleton subclass of GameObject and implementation of PowerUp.
    GameObject
    An abstract class through which all objects in the game inherit from.
    Info
    A constants-only class containing the information which are used across multiple classes in the 'lawnlayer' package.
    Invincible
    A singleton subclass of GameObject and implementation of PowerUp.
    Player
    A singleton subclass of Entity governing the behaviours of the player.
    Shield
    A singleton subclass of GameObject and implementation of PowerUp.
    Tile
    A subclass of GameObject for all tile objects in the game.
    TileList
    A class acting as a container for the Tile objects.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Direction
    An enum indicating the direction the Player is moving in, as well as the orientation of Tiles.
    Info.Name
    An enum containing the pre-defined names of the GameObjects.
    Movement
    An enum indicating the movement of Enemy types.
    Side
    An enum indicating the sides of collision of Enemy types.
